A Shark Crashed From Deep Space | Space Shark | Action Movie

When a meteor crashes on an island beach, it unleashes a deadly alien shark. Now Aleesha, an elite-trained Army staff sergeant on leave, is the only thing standing between the planet and this merciless predator from beyond the stars.

2022.  Stars: Brittany Altenbach, Lukas Silva, Rudon Brannon
